Add responsive UI

PHASE 8 — TESTING & QA

Test each frontend module

Test backend API integration

Fix all edge cases

Conduct full system QA

Fix bugs + re-test

PHASE 9 — DEPLOYMENT

Deploy backend (Render / EC2 / VPS)

Deploy frontend (Vercel / Netlify)

Add custom domain

Add SSL

Configure file storage (AWS S3 or local)

